(38778,'Dinner for Schmucks',69000000,'http://www.dinnerforschmucks.com/','Rising executive Tim Wagner works for a boss who hosts a monthly dinner in which the guest who brings the biggest buffoon gets a career-boost. Tim plans on not attending until he meets Barry, a man who builds dioramas using stuffed mice. Barry''s blundering but good intentions send Tim''s life into a downward spiral, threatening a major business deal and possibly scuttling Tim''s engagement to his fiancee.',11.023691,'2010-07-30',86387857,114,'Released','Takes One To Know One.',5.50,531),
